{"tid":2135111,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"溝通真係好緊要","createTime":"2020-08-01T07:48:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T04:28:59.000Z","uid":47012,"like":5,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ac24ece230319d34c3a7d0a12445b0c6fe41cc","tid":2135111,"uid":47012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:48:25.000Z","msg":"點解我屋企人大部分時間係屋企但係 都好似無乜溝通咁,<br />\n好似我老婆琴日買送,轉登買左舊薑(大概手指公咁大舊) 諗住我今日可以煮個薑蔥蝦球 做餸. 點知佢打比我, 話我老母見我細佬有幾聲咳. 就成舊薑用左黎煲可樂 . 係咁屌我老母, 話佢 不問自取,<br />\n又話細佬 同我老母成日 當佢 唔係自己人 , 乜都根根計較, 成日數住啲餅乾 幾多塊 ,魚蛋幾多粒咁 等嘅閒話, 好似啲野都係我比錢, 不過我都無咁計較啦, 我本身覺得大家作為一家人都可以好好包容 但係 現實就 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , <br />\n我細佬 其實都好生性, 雖然表面上企我老母果邊 但係 有時候都請我老婆食糖, 話曬一家人"},{"pid":"6df82ef01499c2955123af2ece00de5b0f896f6b","tid":2135111,"uid":129800,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"重點喺最後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90284242de352300cfc0e8f71b3eda2066b143d4","tid":2135111,"uid":304619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"買多個舊薑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9cbf52c43b4bb0118e8cfd628f5cae2eb50d8c","tid":2135111,"uid":47012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90284242de352300cfc0e8f71b3eda2066b143d4","tid":2135111,"uid":304619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"買多個舊薑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T07:53:32.000Z","msg":"舊薑唔係重點， 係溝通"},{"pid":"f706423dffc437df717de77ea8143e137798ae52","tid":2135111,"uid":106320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b9cbf52c43b4bb0118e8cfd628f5cae2eb50d8c","tid":2135111,"uid":47012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90284242de352300cfc0e8f71b3eda2066b143d4","tid":2135111,"uid":304619,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T